==================================================
Real-Time Ousia (would) contain these components:

    (+) User interface
        (+) Shell
    (+) Kernel
        (+) Scheduler
        (+) Interrupt Handler
        (+) Memory Management/Protection
        (+) Multitasking
        (-) File System
		(-) Virtual File System
        (+) Device Driver
        (-) Multi Platform Porting
    (-) Communication
	    (-) IP Stack
    (-) Security

	(-) Automation Test Suite
    (*) Build System
	(+) Documentation System


Ps: (*) Has been implemented.
    (-) Hasn't been implemented yet.
    (+) Under developing.

